{"tid":2440042,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港地咁多痴線佬/婆，根本因為醫療資源嚴重不足","createTime":"2021-03-09T16:09:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T04:03:04.000Z","uid":275319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e013b1fb6c99ece965047b7146104d6fd11aa5a3","tid":2440042,"uid":275319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:09:18.000Z","msg":"住過公屋嘅都知<br />\n公屋真係好撚多痴線佬痴線婆<br />\n以前樓下個呀婆每日準時半夜十二點落街發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細個個時靜係知呢啲人有精神病痴撚線<br />\n<br />\n前排因為工作關係接觸咗一啲精神病患者<br />\n了解之後發現佢地咁多年都係不停重複<br />\n<strong>發癲&gt;俾人捉入青山&gt;青山冇位俾人放返出嚟</strong><br />\n醫療資源不足令佢地冇容身之地<br />\n屋企人唔理<br />\n街外人歧視<br />\n醫院冇床位<br />\n公立醫院睇症排期排到癲<br />\n社會上冇人關注佢地保障佢地權益<br />\n所以公屋咪咁多痴線佬周圍發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"orange\">總結 香港真係唔係人住㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"c30bf6b07c44b1d622dc4ea7923ed63546fab547","tid":2440042,"uid":258345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:13:57.000Z","msg":"香港人既精神狀況, 整體黎講都係差啦.<br />\n都唔講運動之前.<br />\n<br />\n而感覺好多人對精神病既了解都係好落後, 仲覺得諗番正少少就解決到."},{"pid":"ccabb1684bd50c82ffce3e2820a129e0a9101de8","tid":2440042,"uid":271303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:14:41.000Z","msg":"正常人住係香港都會屈到有精神病<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91903ac5379adfcc15738164f22f5f8f83e2b6c0","tid":2440042,"uid":173852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T19:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你住過其他地方就知邊度都有痴線佬"},{"pid":"bc296419374f1e8e07d94bd441db3d8326b9a56e","tid":2440042,"uid":275319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c30bf6b07c44b1d622dc4ea7923ed63546fab547","tid":2440042,"uid":258345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:13:57.000Z","msg":"香港人既